  "detailed_description": "\"Circle TD Defence War\" is a tower defense game of the loop type, where players combine dozens of defense towers to create defense tower bonds that enhance their abilities, unlock more skills, and continuously challenge stronger enemies to make the defense tower even stronger! In short, everything you do is to make the defense tower stronger and defeat all enemies!<br><br><i>Defeat the final boss! Win the game!</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Gameplay </h2><br>Before reaching the maximum number of monsters, eliminate them. As long as the monsters do not reach the maximum number, they will walk around the map until they are destroyed!<br>And what you need to do is configure a powerful defense tower firepower network, and combine it with nine player talents to create the most powerful lineup!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Summon Defense Tower </h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100330/extras/6d2a238ca84d7e01436328cdd6eb5517.poster.avif?t=1722426617\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100330/extras/6d2a238ca84d7e01436328cdd6eb5517.webm?t=1722426617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100330/extras/6d2a238ca84d7e01436328cdd6eb5517.mp4?t=1722426617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>After purchasing the defense tower, you can click on the defense tower in the backpack to summon it<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Combination Bonds </h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100330/extras/902366595091886c99cb51905299b302.poster.avif?t=1722426617\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100330/extras/902366595091886c99cb51905299b302.webm?t=1722426617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100330/extras/902366595091886c99cb51905299b302.mp4?t=1722426617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Each defense tower comes with bonds, which can be combined to enhance attributes<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Defense Tower Rising Star </h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100330/extras/00fedbf490bbc5a9c634f4a8929dce77.poster.avif?t=1722426617\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100330/extras/00fedbf490bbc5a9c634f4a8929dce77.webm?t=1722426617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100330/extras/00fedbf490bbc5a9c634f4a8929dce77.mp4?t=1722426617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Having three identical defense towers will upgrade to the next star defense tower<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Equipment synthesis </h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100330/extras/b6035235ddb7650331cbb172cfced2ae.poster.avif?t=1722426617\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100330/extras/b6035235ddb7650331cbb172cfced2ae.webm?t=1722426617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100330/extras/b6035235ddb7650331cbb172cfced2ae.mp4?t=1722426617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Synthesize more powerful equipment in the game based on the introduction of the equipment",
  "about_the_game": "\"Circle TD Defence War\" is a tower defense game of the loop type, where players combine dozens of defense towers to create defense tower bonds that enhance their abilities, unlock more skills, and continuously challenge stronger enemies to make the defense tower even stronger! In short, everything you do is to make the defense tower stronger and defeat all enemies!<br><br><i>Defeat the final boss! Win the game!</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Gameplay </h2><br>Before reaching the maximum number of monsters, eliminate them. As long as the monsters do not reach the maximum number, they will walk around the map until they are destroyed!<br>And what you need to do is configure a powerful defense tower firepower network, and combine it with nine player talents to create the most powerful lineup!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Summon Defense Tower </h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100330/extras/6d2a238ca84d7e01436328cdd6eb5517.poster.avif?t=1722426617\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100330/extras/6d2a238ca84d7e01436328cdd6eb5517.webm?t=1722426617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100330/extras/6d2a238ca84d7e01436328cdd6eb5517.mp4?t=1722426617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>After purchasing the defense tower, you can click on the defense tower in the backpack to summon it<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Combination Bonds </h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100330/extras/902366595091886c99cb51905299b302.poster.avif?t=1722426617\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100330/extras/902366595091886c99cb51905299b302.webm?t=1722426617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100330/extras/902366595091886c99cb51905299b302.mp4?t=1722426617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Each defense tower comes with bonds, which can be combined to enhance attributes<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Defense Tower Rising Star </h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100330/extras/00fedbf490bbc5a9c634f4a8929dce77.poster.avif?t=1722426617\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100330/extras/00fedbf490bbc5a9c634f4a8929dce77.webm?t=1722426617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100330/extras/00fedbf490bbc5a9c634f4a8929dce77.mp4?t=1722426617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Having three identical defense towers will upgrade to the next star defense tower<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Equipment synthesis </h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100330/extras/b6035235ddb7650331cbb172cfced2ae.poster.avif?t=1722426617\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100330/extras/b6035235ddb7650331cbb172cfced2ae.webm?t=1722426617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100330/extras/b6035235ddb7650331cbb172cfced2ae.mp4?t=1722426617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Synthesize more powerful equipment in the game based on the introduction of the equipment",
